<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_140390"><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote">引用</div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote"> 这个....<br>用英文+旧版的翻译慢慢推.....<br><br>恩，话说我刚才还真找到一个翻译好的技能... </blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div> 请给下连接看看 </div>
